    <Description>CR: 1872570 Add Display Screen Size Enum for Info 3.5C in MY21 Display_Screen_Size .Per CR##1919275 add new calibration RVS_RIDE_HEIGHT_GUIDELINE_ADJUSTMENT_AVAIL </Description>
    <Author>Evelyn Job</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
