    <Description>CR 1738298 Added Transparent Hood View (RVS_FEATURE_AVAIL_TRANSPARENT_HOOD_VIEW) to Function Driver Display - Viewing System Info 3.5c Requirements - Section 2.2.1 Configuration</Description>
    <Author>Jason Heitman</Author>
